perience study guides encourage learning and reflection in the arts beyond the performance and are provided free of charge to all classrooms attending matinees stanford school of education partnership brings teacher candidates in the stanford teacher education program step and their k 12 students from local public schools to lively arts matinee performances free of charge and underscores the importance of arts education for stanford's pre service teachers stanford lively arts the palo alto unified school district and theatreworks silicon valley are members of the partners in education program of the john f kennedy center for the performing arts selected in recognition of their demonstrated commitment to arts education the members of the partnership team collaborate on advocacy efforts and programs serving the teachers and students of the palo alto unified school district programs for families lively arts family friendly fare brings a diversity of art forms to children and adults in the 2011 12 season including diavolo dance company january 28 and word for word performing arts company february 17 performances are generally on weekends and lively arts offers tickets at a 50 discount to all events for ages 18 and under k 12 family friendly programs programs for community partners stanford lively arts is proud to partner with the following schools and community organizations to provide specially designed programs and performance opportunities for children youth adults and families in the vibrant community in which we live boys and girls clubs of the peninsula child advocates of silicon valley college track of east palo alto community school of music and arts eastside college preparatory school hope house palo alto unified school district flickr sets rennie harris student matinee grades 3 12 rennie harris student matinee grades 3 12 gamelan cudamani student matinee gamelan cudamani student matinee la theater works student matinee la theater works student matinee romeo & 